reactor.core.publisher

类 WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.core.publisher.WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Type of dispatched signal
    封闭类:
    WorkQueueProcessor<E>

    public static final class WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T>
extends Object
    WorkQueueProcessor builder that can be used to create new processors. Instantiate it through the WorkQueueProcessor.builder() static method:

    WorkQueueProcessor<String> processor = WorkQueueProcessor.<String>builder().build()

    • 方法详细资料

      • name

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> name(@Nullable
                                          String name)
        Configures name for this builder. Default value is WorkQueueProcessor. Name is push to default if the provided name is null.
        参数:
        name - Use a new cached ExecutorService and assign this name to the created threads if executor(ExecutorService) is not configured.
        返回:
        builder with provided name

      • bufferSize

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> bufferSize(int bufferSize)
        Configures buffer size for this builder. Default value is Queues.SMALL_BUFFER_SIZE.
        参数:
        bufferSize - the internal buffer size to hold signals, must be a power of 2
        返回:
        builder with provided buffer size

      • waitStrategy

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> waitStrategy(@Nullable
                                                  WaitStrategy waitStrategy)
        Configures wait strategy for this builder. Default value is WaitStrategy.liteBlocking(). Wait strategy is push to default if the provided waitStrategy is null.
        参数:
        waitStrategy - A RingBuffer WaitStrategy to use instead of the default smart blocking wait strategy.
        返回:
        builder with provided wait strategy

      • autoCancel

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> autoCancel(boolean autoCancel)
        Configures auto-cancel for this builder. Default value is true.
        参数:
        autoCancel - automatically cancel
        返回:
        builder with provided auto-cancel

      • executor

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> executor(@Nullable
                                              ExecutorService executor)
        Configures an ExecutorService to execute as many event-loop consuming the ringbuffer as subscribers. Name configured using name(String) will be ignored if executor is push.
        参数:
        executor - A provided ExecutorService to manage threading infrastructure
        返回:
        builder with provided executor

      • requestTaskExecutor

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> requestTaskExecutor(@Nullable
                                                         ExecutorService requestTaskExecutor)
        Configures an additional ExecutorService that is used internally on each subscription.
        参数:
        requestTaskExecutor - internal request executor
        返回:
        builder with provided internal request executor

      • share

        public WorkQueueProcessor.Builder<T> share(boolean share)
        Configures sharing state for this builder. A shared Processor authorizes concurrent onNext calls and is suited for multi-threaded publisher that will fan-in data.
        参数:
        share - true to support concurrent onNext calls
        返回:
        builder with specified sharing

      • build

        public WorkQueueProcessor<T> build()
        Creates a new WorkQueueProcessor using the properties of this builder.
        返回:
        a fresh processor
